hatexmpp is a xmpp-client featuring ii-like interface (xmppfs really)

deps: glib (~>=2.18.4), fuse (~>=2.7.4), loudmouth (~>=1.4.3)

synopsis: ./hatexmpp <mountpoint> [-d]

to get the fresht one, use 'git clone git://github.com/l29ah/hatexmpp.git'

to scream, go to hatexmpp@conference.jabber.ru

to autotest, do 'make test'

